      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Ismail, from Al-Fazl Bin Sh<span class=\"iTxt\">Azaan</span>, from Safwan Bin Yahya, from Mansour Bin Hazim, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The seeking of Forgiveness in <span class=\"iTxt\">Al-Witr </span>(Salāt) is seventy times’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "33. Muhammad ibn ’Isma‘il has narrated from al-Fadl ibn Shadhan from Safwan ibn Yahya from Mansur ibn Hazim who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said that in al-Witr, ask forgiveness from Allah seventy times.” (Ahadith 20-34 are best explained in the form of fatwa.) "
        ]
      }
